name: Bark! The Herald Angels Sing
description: It's a warm (litterally) tropical Christmas here in Ubud, Bali. Green and red color combination everywhere presented by the Heliconias, big Christmas tree-shaped Balinese buildings, and a choir of dogs, frogs, ducks, and cicadas under the bright stars :D Definitely not a white Christmas, but have a jolly one, peace on earth, peace within our hearts. Rahajeng Natal, damai di bumi, damai di hati.
